{"tid":456370,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾夫拿企圖襲擊看台上 支持法國馬賽球迷被逐","createTime":"2017-11-03T02:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T07:15:39.000Z","uid":10338,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"ff23bdc5cc2c4811808292230a885b1ae29946b8","tid":456370,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T02:14:28.000Z","msg":"法國馬賽球員艾夫拿與支持馬賽的球迷衝突，並企圖襲擊看台上觀眾。<br />\n<br />\n當時馬賽在葡萄牙與甘馬雷斯進行歐霸盃分組賽。目擊者表示，現年36歲的艾夫拿在後備席範圍，與大約500名馬賽球迷爭執，其後企圖凌空飛踢看台上觀眾。在場工作人員將雙方分隔，艾夫拿亦被球證驅逐出場。<br />\n<br />\n在1995年，效力曼聯的法國球員簡東拿亦同樣與在場球迷衝突，導致簡東拿被英格蘭足總判罰停賽九個月。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1362780_1_L_20171103061843.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1362780_1_L_20171103061843.jpg&h=20cb01ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fb33e4d58c69ceec6ea63e0b869583cdced4cf6","tid":456370,"uid":26959,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T02:19:48.000Z","msg":"踢鳩你咪踢鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好出奇? 大驚小怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cdb1a89f0258943026b210de80f8e2f5e85b75","tid":456370,"uid":18669,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T02:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DNqaZe2X0AAmpX-.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDNqaZe2X0AAmpX-.jpg&h=f7a33a5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賓周馬都在場"},{"pid":"2cfe442ec65952d5300b6323ef05859c3ffe5c6b","tid":456370,"uid":39710,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T02:21:14.000Z","msg":"寫到佢一挑500咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目擊者表示，現年36歲的艾夫拿在後備席範圍，與大約500名馬賽球迷爭執，其後企圖凌空飛踢看台上觀眾。在場工作人員將雙方分隔，艾夫拿亦被球證驅逐出場。"},{"pid":"5fab12f2ad5b1cc85238ea67e904f8f4eb9d691b","tid":456370,"uid":19126,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T02:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫到佢一挑500咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目擊者表示，現年36歲的艾夫拿在後備席範圍，與大約500名馬賽球迷爭執，其後企圖凌空飛踢看台上觀眾。在場工作人員將雙方分隔，艾夫拿亦被球證驅逐出場。</blockquote><br />\n一腳踢500人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004b1bff3c014ad44acfb31796c3ea10a1ef3415","tid":456370,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da85ce8d33989d07a8ab9de8ccd65d5384b942d","tid":456370,"uid":52006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T02:39:35.000Z","msg":"魔性澎湃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369839f46e41efb279fb8fb8cb2772923d856bde","tid":456370,"uid":18384,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T02:42:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DNqaZe2X0AAmpX-.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDNqaZe2X0AAmpX-.jpg&h=f7a33a5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賓周馬都在場</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc905424de2227a42edef471b521ff4a92ecee03","tid":456370,"uid":25582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T02:45:40.000Z","msg":"有冇片"},{"pid":"6cfb722b16cbd7b0257e020694666c02035c1c3e","tid":456370,"uid":10503,"like":1,"d